@startuml UC5_SearchSortFilterBorrowedDevices

title UC5 - Search / Sort / Filter Borrowed Devices (Simple Sequence)

actor User
participant UI
participant System
database Database

User -> UI : Enter search / select sort / filter
UI -> System : Request filtered borrowed devices
System -> Database : Query borrowed devices with conditions
Database --> System : Return filtered list
System --> UI : Send filtered borrowed devices
UI --> User : Display updated list

@enduml
